/* Welcome / About */
"I live in the menu bar and keep your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working — then let it sleep when they stop.\n\nThere's nothing to set up. Look for the bolt in the menu bar." = "我住在菜单栏里，会在 Codex 或 Claude Code 工作时让你的 Mac 保持唤醒，工作结束后再让它休眠。\n\n无需任何设置。在菜单栏中找闪电图标即可。";
"Get Started" = "开始使用";
"Version %@\n\nKeeps your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working.\n\nLid-closed mode adds one narrow sudoers rule for the exact pmset commands it needs, and backs off automatically if your Mac gets too warm. Remove it anytime from Advanced." = "版本 %@\n\n在 Codex 或 Claude Code 工作时让你的 Mac 保持唤醒。\n\n合盖模式只会为其所需的特定 pmset 命令添加一条范围很窄的 sudoers 规则，并在 Mac 过热时自动停止。你可以随时在“高级”中移除它。";
"OK" = "好";

